OL,3,CTerrorist turned spy
OL,5,FFrederico Scappaticci grew up in the
OL,6,FRepublican heartland of the Markets in
OL,7,Fsouth Belfast.
OL,9,FBy his early 20s, the son of an
OL,10,FItalian immigrant was bricklaying by
OL,11,Fday, but at night was building a
OL,12,Freputation within the Provisional IRA.
OL,14,FScapattici's rise through the ranks of
OL,15,Fthe IRA saw him tasked with hunting
OL,16,Fdown informants with the much-feared
OL,17,F'internal security unit', nicknamed
OL,18,Fthe 'nutting squad'.
OL,20,FBut we now know he was the biggest spy
OL,21,Fof them all.
