OL,5,FScappaticci ended up in west Belfast.
OL,6,FMuch has changed, but stories of his
OL,7,Fruthlessness are still talked about.
OL,9,FMany of his victims were abducted from
OL,10,Fhere, tortured in safe houses and
OL,11,Fbarns close to the border and then
OL,12,Fexecuted.
OL,14,FThe victim's body was often dumped in
OL,15,Fa ditch, in alleyways or on the
OL,16,Froadside as a warning to others
OL,17,Fsuspected of talking to the enemy.
