OL,5,F"He was arrested, and I think it was
OL,6,Fdrunk driving. The strange thing was
OL,7,Fthat very very quickly people came in
OL,8,Fcivvies and took this person away and
OL,9,Fthey were all instructed not to
OL,10,Fmention what had happened, and make no
OL,11,Frecord of it, but the corporal thought
OL,12,Fit was really interesting because the
OL,13,Fguy's name was Scappaticci."
OL,15,FProtected at all costs - even in death.
